00:12:18,240 --> 00:12:19,710
make this will valid?

284
00:12:20,400 --> 00:12:22,530
Mr. Wang, were you present at the time?

285
00:12:22,540 --> 00:12:24,030
Was there a notary there?

286
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:26,010
Your father's will has always

287
00:12:26,010 --> 00:12:27,890
been handled by another lawyer.

288
00:12:28,340 --> 00:12:29,720
After Mr. Lin passed away,

289
00:12:29,720 --> 00:12:31,480
that lawyer left our firm

290
00:12:31,480 --> 00:12:32,480
and disappeared.

291
00:12:33,080 --> 00:12:33,960
I'm so sorry.

292
00:12:35,390 --> 00:12:38,120
The lawyer disappears
at such a critical moment.

293
00:12:40,600 --> 00:12:41,730
What a coincidence.

294
00:12:43,360 --> 00:12:44,240
Mr. Wang,

295
00:12:45,050 --> 00:12:46,560
I want to sue Lin Jinghan.

296
00:12:47,910 --> 00:12:49,610
I will not recognize this will.

297
00:12:49,610 --> 00:12:51,490
[Six Arts Hall]

298
00:12:51,510 --> 00:12:53,860
[Ju De Hall Restaurant]

299
00:12:53,790 --> 00:12:55,590
Can't you really take this case?

300
00:12:57,030 --> 00:13:00,090
You're one of the most
well-known lawyers in Shanghai.

301
00:13:01,310 --> 00:13:03,070
In the short time we've been sitting here,

302
00:13:03,070 --> 00:13:04,360
Lin Siyun has already seen

303
00:13:04,360 --> 00:13:05,480
5 lawyers.

304
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:07,500
Even Lawyer Xie turned it down.

305
00:13:07,540 --> 00:13:08,870
I doubt anyone in Shanghai

306
00:13:08,870 --> 00:13:10,280
will dare take it.

307
00:13:10,990 --> 00:13:12,390
I wonder who she's trying

308
00:13:12,390 --> 00:13:13,550
to sue anyway.

309
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,200
Based on my experience,

310
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:17,670
your chances of
winning this case are very low.

311
00:13:17,670 --> 00:13:18,290
I'm sorry.

312
00:13:23,120 --> 00:13:24,920
Miss Lin's family
has fallen on hard times—

313
00:13:24,920 --> 00:13:25,920
she has no way out.

314
00:13:27,000 --> 00:13:28,120
But she's strong.

315
00:13:28,260 --> 00:13:29,330
I admire

316
00:13:29,630 --> 00:13:31,000
women like her.

317
00:13:35,630 --> 00:13:36,160
Cheng Ao,

318
00:13:36,510 --> 00:13:37,910
do you feel sorry for her?

319
00:13:39,390 --> 00:13:40,200
Yes, I do.

320
00:13:40,790 --> 00:13:42,250
But with her personality,

321
00:13:42,340 --> 00:13:43,790
I don't think she needs anyone's pity.

322
00:13:43,790 --> 00:13:45,470
How do you know
what her personality's like?

323
00:13:45,470 --> 00:13:46,550
We had coffee.

324
00:13:47,790 --> 00:13:48,630
Where?

325
00:13:48,840 --> 00:13:50,040
Upstairs yesterday.

326
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:50,940
What's wrong?

327
00:13:52,310 --> 00:13:54,820
I've never even had coffee upstairs.

328
00:13:55,640 --> 00:13:56,640
You should try it.

329
00:13:57,440 --> 00:13:58,390
I meant with you.

330
00:14:08,670 --> 00:14:09,460
Mrs. Shen,

331
00:14:10,320 --> 00:14:12,380
I once read your interview in the paper,

332
00:14:12,380 --> 00:14:13,000
where you said

333
00:14:13,000 --> 00:14:14,720
that the progress of Chinese society

334
00:14:14,720 --> 00:14:17,270
must start with
the standing of Chinese women.

335
00:14:17,270 --> 00:14:19,080
If Chinese women have no standing,

336
00:14:19,080 --> 00:14:19,480
then

337
00:14:19,480 --> 00:14:20,380
Chinese society

338
00:14:20,380 --> 00:14:21,870
will have no future either.

339
00:14:21,870 --> 00:14:22,930
Yes, I did say that.

340
00:14:23,290 --> 00:14:24,820
You remember it so clearly.

341
00:14:25,550 --> 00:14:28,150
Many great thinkers
have said similar things.

342
00:14:28,480 --> 00:14:29,030
But

343
00:14:29,090 --> 00:14:30,840
the way you put it
was simple and powerful,

344
00:14:30,840 --> 00:14:32,030
and very moving.

345
00:14:32,150 --> 00:14:32,880
Impressive.

346
00:14:34,960 --> 00:14:37,160
So you all think Lin Siyun is great, huh?

347
00:14:38,790 --> 00:14:40,250
Who's prettier, me or her?

348
00:14:43,790 --> 00:14:45,240
Of course you are.

349
00:14:45,270 --> 00:14:46,400
I wasn't asking you.

350
00:14:46,720 --> 00:14:47,390
You tell me.

351
00:14:47,790 --> 00:14:48,670
Lin Siyun.

352
00:14:51,570 --> 00:14:53,900
Do people in your group have bad taste

353
00:14:54,600 --> 00:14:55,840
or just bad eyesight?

354
00:14:55,960 --> 00:14:56,920
Probably both.

355
00:15:07,120 --> 00:15:08,250
I have another case.

356
00:15:08,420 --> 00:15:09,390
Excuse me,

357
00:15:09,910 --> 00:15:10,770
enjoy your tea.

358
00:15:11,550 --> 00:15:12,580
Bye, Mr. Cheng.

359
00:15:18,030 --> 00:15:18,790
Yingying,

360
00:15:19,030 --> 00:15:20,630
what's wrong with you today?

361
00:15:20,700 --> 00:15:22,230
I've always been like this.

362
00:15:23,120 --> 00:15:24,120
And Cheng Ao—

363
00:15:24,120 --> 00:15:26,120
he contradicted everything I said.

364
00:15:28,370 --> 00:15:30,570
Did he act like this because he likes me?

365
00:15:31,480 --> 00:15:32,270
Aunt Nan.

366
00:15:35,980 --> 00:15:36,860
Maybe.

367
00:15:42,900 --> 00:15:43,690
Miss Lin.

368
00:15:45,910 --> 00:15:47,370
I've been waiting for you.

369
00:15:47,720 --> 00:15:48,390
I was thinking...

370
00:15:48,390 --> 00:15:49,790
I was looking for you too.

371
00:15:51,910 --> 00:15:52,750
Looking for me?

372
00:15:52,750 --> 00:15:54,350
If you want to file a lawsuit,

373
00:15:54,560 --> 00:15:55,620
you can consult me.

374
00:15:58,150 --> 00:15:59,000
Thank you.

375
00:16:00,880 --> 00:16:02,210
Let's talk in my office.

376
00:16:05,790 --> 00:16:07,200
I want to sue my brother.

377
00:16:07,730 --> 00:16:10,140
Lin Jinghan is suspected of forging a will

378
00:16:10,390 --> 00:16:13,320
and seizing property
that belongs to me and my niece.

379
00:16:14,460 --> 00:16:16,120
What did Xie and those lawyers

380
00:16:16,400 --> 00:16:17,190
say just now?

381
00:16:20,200 --> 00:16:21,120
They said

382
00:16:22,030 --> 00:16:23,760
since I broke off my engagement

383
00:16:24,000 --> 00:16:25,860
and now want to sue my own brother,

384
00:16:26,150 --> 00:16:27,360
I have a bad reputation

385
00:16:27,360 --> 00:16:28,600
among the upper class

386
00:16:28,750 --> 00:16:29,790
in Shanghai.

387
00:16:30,790 --> 00:16:32,650
Any lawyer with a shred of dignity

388
00:16:33,120 --> 00:16:34,720
would refuse to take my case.

389
00:16:38,000 --> 00:16:38,800
I'll help you.

390
00:16:44,510 --> 00:16:45,320
Thank you.

391
00:16:51,150 --> 00:16:52,810
Can you afford the legal fees?

392
00:16:55,200 --> 00:16:56,030
How much?

393
00:16:56,510 --> 00:16:58,170
I charge 3 times what Xie does.

394
00:17:04,470 --> 00:17:05,930
Can I pay in installments?

395
00:17:13,770 --> 00:17:15,170
Let's win the case first.

396
00:17:25,859 --> 00:17:26,910
Lin Siyun.

397
00:17:34,829 --> 00:17:35,329
Mom.

398
00:17:36,430 --> 00:17:38,560
Why aren't you in bed yet? It's so late.

399
00:17:38,960 --> 00:17:40,090
I need to talk to you.

400
00:17:53,400 --> 00:17:55,660
Are you really going to sue your brother?

401
00:17:56,400 --> 00:17:56,970
Yes.

402
00:17:58,030 --> 00:17:59,400
It's not too late

403
00:17:59,680 --> 00:18:00,880
to change your mind.

404
00:18:02,880 --> 00:18:05,540
Your fourth aunt will come
pick you up tomorrow.

405
00:18:06,720 --> 00:18:08,030
We're still family.

406
00:18:11,830 --> 00:18:13,160
I'm not going to Suzhou.

407
00:18:14,200 --> 00:18:15,600
I'm staying in Shanghai,

408
00:18:16,720 --> 00:18:18,030
staying in this house.

409
00:18:19,440 --> 00:18:20,400
This is my home.

410
00:18:21,790 --> 00:18:23,080
My father left it to me.

411
00:18:23,100 --> 00:18:24,380
Your father is dead.

412
00:18:24,410 --> 00:18:25,480
I'm still alive.

413
00:18:30,270 --> 00:18:31,270
From now on,

414
00:18:35,070 --> 00:18:36,730
you're no longer my daughter.

415
00:18:41,270 --> 00:18:41,830
Fine.

416
00:18:50,190 --> 00:18:51,560
You're not

417
00:18:52,480 --> 00:18:53,880
just selfish,

418
00:18:55,360 --> 00:18:57,270
also cruel and vicious.

419
00:18:57,880 --> 00:19:00,080
Think of me however you like.

420
00:19:00,790 --> 00:19:01,960
Don't you forget.

421
00:19:02,270 --> 00:19:03,790
I gave birth to you

422
00:19:03,790 --> 00:19:05,390
and raised you to who you are.

423
00:19:06,860 --> 00:19:08,520
Have you lost all conscience?

424
00:19:10,350 --> 00:19:11,680
You ungrateful wretch.

425
00:19:11,830 --> 00:19:13,940
If I had known you'd turn out like this,

426
00:19:13,940 --> 00:19:15,940
I should've strangled you long ago!

427
00:19:20,640 --> 00:19:21,900
If saying these things

428
00:19:23,230 --> 00:19:24,490
makes you feel better,

429
00:19:25,960 --> 00:19:26,960
then go ahead.

430
00:19:27,920 --> 00:19:29,760
I have nothing more to say to you.

431
00:19:33,230 --> 00:19:34,130
Get out!

432
00:20:06,070 --> 00:20:06,920
[Father,]

433
00:20:07,510 --> 00:20:08,710
[Brother and Mother]

434
00:20:08,920 --> 00:20:10,510
[both call me selfish.]

435
00:20:11,070 --> 00:20:11,940
[Am I selfish]

436
00:20:12,490 --> 00:20:13,820
[for doing this?]

437
00:20:14,570 --> 00:20:16,030
[You always supported me]

438
00:20:16,070 --> 00:20:17,400
[in becoming a doctor,]

439
00:20:17,590 --> 00:20:19,030
[helping patients,]

440
00:20:19,270 --> 00:20:20,870
[building my own hospital.]

441
00:20:21,680 --> 00:20:22,720
[I don't believe]

442
00:20:23,030 --> 00:20:25,400
[that will was written by yourself.]

443
00:20:26,640 --> 00:20:28,030
[I'm not fighting]

444
00:20:28,590 --> 00:20:30,120
[this lawsuit for myself.]

445
00:20:30,540 --> 00:20:32,140
[You must understand that.]

446
00:20:37,360 --> 00:20:38,040
Aunt.

447
00:20:48,680 --> 00:20:50,080
Aunt, why are you crying?

448
00:20:50,590 --> 00:20:51,880
Don't be sad.

449
00:20:52,240 --> 00:20:53,400
I'm not crying,

450
00:20:53,610 --> 00:20:54,750
and I'm not sad.

451
00:20:56,040 --> 00:20:57,610
Why are you coming to see me

452
00:20:57,750 --> 00:20:58,790
so late at night?

453
00:20:59,180 --> 00:21:01,510
Aunt, I support you
in filing the lawsuit.

454
00:21:02,910 --> 00:21:05,150
Don't worry about the lawsuit.

455
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,640
Just focus on your studies,

456
00:21:06,640 --> 00:21:07,970
and when you finish middle school,

457
00:21:07,970 --> 00:21:09,900
I'll send you abroad to study.

458
00:21:09,930 --> 00:21:11,730
You can study whatever you want.

459
00:21:14,360 --> 00:21:16,210
This is the New Year's money I've saved.

460
00:21:16,210 --> 00:21:17,540
Take it for the lawsuit.

461
00:21:17,720 --> 00:21:19,050
We'll definitely win.

462
00:21:25,270 --> 00:21:26,070
Thank you, Yi.

463
00:21:49,220 --> 00:21:51,230
[Disgraced socialite sues her
own brother over inheritance.]

464
00:21:51,230 --> 00:21:53,250
[Will it repeat the scandal
of the Sheng siblings' feud in 1928?]

465
00:21:59,230 --> 00:22:00,160
I've checked it.

466
00:22:01,350 --> 00:22:02,350
Your house's

467
00:22:02,440 --> 00:22:03,680
sale contract

468
00:22:03,720 --> 00:22:04,730
was never signed.

469
00:22:05,920 --> 00:22:08,520
I terminated the deal
on grounds of illegality.

470
00:22:08,520 --> 00:22:09,650
Here are the papers.

471
00:22:13,500 --> 00:22:15,300
[Termination of Sale Application]

472
00:22:16,590 --> 00:22:17,720
You said your father

473
00:22:17,950 --> 00:22:19,320
was an open-minded man,

474
00:22:19,350 --> 00:22:21,390
never favored sons over daughters.

475
00:22:21,410 --> 00:22:22,140
Is that true?

476
00:22:25,680 --> 00:22:26,480
Yes.

477
00:22:26,820 --> 00:22:28,280
My father loved me dearly.

478
00:22:28,500 --> 00:22:30,700
He supported everything I wanted to do.

479
00:22:33,350 --> 00:22:36,280
I found this while
searching through the documents.

480
00:22:39,670 --> 00:22:41,900
[From Miss Sheng's
Lawsuit Against Her Brother:]

481
00:22:41,900 --> 00:22:44,130
[The Awakening of Women's
Consciousness in the Republic Era]

482
00:22:44,830 --> 00:22:45,890
"West River Moon?"

483
00:22:47,200 --> 00:22:48,860
That was my father's pen name.

484
00:22:49,540 --> 00:22:51,490
Your father had been

485
00:22:51,920 --> 00:22:54,250
openly supporting Miss Sheng in her case,

486
00:22:54,590 --> 00:22:55,550
which shows

487
00:22:56,330 --> 00:22:59,330
he was never someone
who favored sons over daughters.

488
00:23:04,680 --> 00:23:05,520
Do you think

489
00:23:06,200 --> 00:23:07,720
Lin Jinghan's will

490
00:23:08,680 --> 00:23:10,200
could possibly be forged?

491
00:23:10,260 --> 00:23:12,460
I can't prove it's forged at the moment,

492
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:14,940
but he can't prove it's genuine either.

493
00:23:14,940 --> 00:23:15,530
First,

494
00:23:15,860 --> 00:23:17,460
there was no notary present.

495
00:23:17,740 --> 00:23:18,200
Second,

496
00:23:18,960 --> 00:23:20,720
only the signature is your father's.

497
00:23:20,720 --> 00:23:22,470
The text was written by someone else,

498
00:23:22,470 --> 00:23:24,130
which isn't very convincing.

499
00:23:24,610 --> 00:23:26,320
The will is full of flaws,

500
00:23:27,550 --> 00:23:28,640
yet Lin Jinghan

501
00:23:28,880 --> 00:23:30,480
doesn't seem worried at all.

502
00:23:31,090 --> 00:23:31,960
I'm afraid

503
00:23:32,230 --> 00:23:34,090
he might have ties with the judge.

504
00:23:36,340 --> 00:23:37,210
That's why we

505
00:23:37,510 --> 00:23:39,230
can't put all our hopes

506
00:23:39,310 --> 00:23:40,550
on the courtroom.

507
00:23:42,830 --> 00:23:44,200
If not in court,

508
00:23:46,200 --> 00:23:48,440
then what can we do outside of it?

509
00:23:50,480 --> 00:23:51,480
Outside of court,

510
00:23:53,550 --> 00:23:54,590
we could dance.

511
00:23:55,070 --> 00:23:55,680
Dance?

512
00:23:57,960 --> 00:23:59,420
How would dancing with you

513
00:23:59,640 --> 00:24:00,920
help with

514
00:24:01,280 --> 00:24:02,370
this case?

515
00:24:02,550 --> 00:24:03,590
Dancing with me

516
00:24:04,270 --> 00:24:05,550
won't help

517
00:24:06,270 --> 00:24:07,330
the case directly.

518
00:24:10,160 --> 00:24:11,360
What do you mean then?

519
00:24:11,590 --> 00:24:12,310
But

520
00:24:12,790 --> 00:24:13,990
in certain settings,

521
00:24:14,720 --> 00:24:15,780
it might be useful.

522
00:24:19,130 --> 00:24:21,110
There's a charity gala this Sunday.

523
00:24:21,110 --> 00:24:23,300
Many influential women will be there.

524
00:24:24,000 --> 00:24:26,070
Mrs. Shen's charity gala?

525
00:24:26,270 --> 00:24:27,070
Exactly.

526
00:24:27,590 --> 00:24:29,720
Mrs. Shen is a very progressive woman.

527
00:24:29,860 --> 00:24:31,690
If you talk with her,

528
00:24:32,340 --> 00:24:33,850
I believe she'll understand

529
00:24:33,850 --> 00:24:34,780
and support you.

530
00:24:37,680 --> 00:24:39,170
I see.

531
00:24:40,200 --> 00:24:41,310
You want

532
00:24:41,750 --> 00:24:43,640
these progressive women

533
00:24:44,000 --> 00:24:45,600
to support me in their own way

534
00:24:45,940 --> 00:24:47,690
for this lawsuit.

535
00:24:47,770 --> 00:24:48,570
Smart.

536
00:24:50,110 --> 00:24:52,170
I don't think I need to dance with you.

537
00:24:54,200 --> 00:24:55,240
As for dancing,

538
00:24:57,590 --> 00:24:58,520
that's up to you.

539
00:25:20,270 --> 00:25:22,840
I find it so hard to talk to you.

540
00:25:23,790 --> 00:25:24,510
Pillager.

541
00:25:24,560 --> 00:25:25,270
Come in.

542
00:25:28,110 --> 00:25:28,900
Sit.

543
00:25:30,080 --> 00:25:30,920
Get out.

544
00:25:30,940 --> 00:25:32,070
I didn't invite you.

545
00:25:33,080 --> 00:25:34,570
What kind of attitude is that?

546
00:25:34,570 --> 00:25:35,710
Siyun is my good friend.

547
00:25:35,710 --> 00:25:36,990
Show some respect.

548
00:25:37,210 --> 00:25:38,690
This gala is hosted by Aunt Nan.

549
00:25:38,690 --> 00:25:39,720
So what?

550
00:25:39,740 --> 00:25:41,170
Why don't you go outside with her

551
00:25:41,170 --> 00:25:42,200
and have a private chat?

552
00:25:42,200 --> 00:25:43,200
Where are we supposed to go?

553
00:25:43,200 --> 00:25:44,590
Aunt Nan paid for this. Did you?

554
00:25:44,590 --> 00:25:45,400
You never stop

555
00:25:45,400 --> 00:25:46,070
talking about money.

556
00:25:46,070 --> 00:25:46,790
Moneygrubber.

557
00:25:46,790 --> 00:25:47,240
I just don't get it.

558
00:25:47,240 --> 00:25:48,070
I'm your sister.

559
00:25:48,070 --> 00:25:49,270
So you do remember you're my sister.

560
00:25:49,270 --> 00:25:49,960
Why are you always picking on me?

561
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:50,790
You're so nice to her,

562
00:25:50,790 --> 00:25:51,790
but does she even care about you?

563
00:25:51,790 --> 00:25:53,350
Whether she cares about me is between us.

564
00:25:53,350 --> 00:25:54,350
I'm done talking to you.

565
00:25:54,350 --> 00:25:55,480
You always upset me.

566
00:25:56,850 --> 00:25:58,110
You can talk sometime.

567
00:26:10,420 --> 00:26:11,820
Come on, make some space.

568
00:26:29,480 --> 00:26:30,310
Qiao Shijun.

569
00:26:30,460 --> 00:26:31,310
Come in.

570
00:26:31,690 --> 00:26:32,490
Sit here.

571
00:26:36,920 --> 00:26:37,730
Stand up.

572
00:26:42,070 --> 00:26:42,870
Mr. Qiao,

573
00:26:43,070 --> 00:26:44,200
tell us

574
