728
00:34:52,840 --> 00:34:54,000
You just said

729
00:34:54,170 --> 00:34:55,650
you only care about

730
00:34:56,070 --> 00:34:57,219
your family affairs,

731
00:34:57,219 --> 00:34:59,000
