00:41:20,600 --> 00:41:21,790
Mrs. Lin isn't sick at all.

860
00:41:21,790 --> 00:41:23,100
He told me to say so.

861
00:41:25,320 --> 00:41:26,200
I see.

862
00:41:30,090 --> 00:41:31,290
Thank you, Director.

863
00:41:37,440 --> 00:41:38,190
Good for you.

864
00:41:40,410 --> 00:41:41,210
Fine.

865
00:41:44,640 --> 00:41:45,370
Even if

866
00:41:46,190 --> 00:41:47,850
I made that up about my mother,

867
00:41:48,010 --> 00:41:49,540
you just heard it yourself,

868
00:41:49,730 --> 00:41:51,320
my sister doesn't want anything.

869
00:41:51,320 --> 00:41:52,630
All the property goes to me.

870
00:41:52,630 --> 00:41:54,160
She's the concerned party,

871
00:41:54,390 --> 00:41:56,270
and you have to follow her wish.

872
00:41:56,400 --> 00:41:57,760
I really can't.

873
00:41:59,110 --> 00:42:00,070
Mr. Lin,

874
00:42:01,370 --> 00:42:02,900
this case is going to trial.

875
00:42:05,690 --> 00:42:07,400
Are you just looking for trouble?

876
00:42:07,400 --> 00:42:08,800
What's wrong with you?

877
00:42:08,800 --> 00:42:09,400
Are you just...

878
00:42:09,400 --> 00:42:11,330
Who do you think you're talking to?

879
00:42:11,330 --> 00:42:12,230
Don't come any closer!

880
00:42:12,230 --> 00:42:13,060
Stay back!

881
00:42:13,090 --> 00:42:14,250
I've trained, you know.

882
00:42:14,250 --> 00:42:15,960
Aren't you guys lawyers?

883
00:42:16,810 --> 00:42:18,330
Mr. Cheng is a lawyer.

884
00:42:19,010 --> 00:42:19,890
I'm not.

885
00:42:20,430 --> 00:42:21,950
What do you do then?

886
00:42:24,440 --> 00:42:25,370
My name is Cheng,

887
00:42:25,800 --> 00:42:26,760
from the Zeng's.

888
00:42:27,100 --> 00:42:28,430
You better check it out.

889
00:42:28,500 --> 00:42:30,430
It's the same Zeng you owe money to.

890
00:42:31,920 --> 00:42:32,670
Boss,

891
00:42:32,840 --> 00:42:34,230
what's it gonna be—arm or leg?

892
00:42:34,230 --> 00:42:35,280
Ask Mr. Lin.

893
00:42:36,190 --> 00:42:36,880
Mr. Lin,

894
00:42:37,280 --> 00:42:38,070
pick one.

895
00:42:38,670 --> 00:42:40,380
Arm or leg?

896
00:42:41,170 --> 00:42:43,030
I'm asking you. Arm or leg?

897
00:42:47,810 --> 00:42:48,970
Sorry about that, Mr. Lin.

898
00:42:48,970 --> 00:42:49,830
It went off accidentally.

899
00:42:49,830 --> 00:42:51,430
I'll settle.

900
00:42:52,520 --> 00:42:53,120
Mr. Cheng,

901
00:42:53,390 --> 00:42:54,450
I...

902
00:42:54,480 --> 00:42:55,690
I'll never bully my sister again.

903
00:42:55,690 --> 00:42:56,720
I'll give her back her share

904
00:42:56,720 --> 00:42:58,050
of the estate right now.

905
00:42:58,280 --> 00:42:59,480
Is that okay with you?

906
00:43:03,270 --> 00:43:04,870
I'm okay if you say it's okay.

907
00:43:05,430 --> 00:43:06,280
It's up to you.

908
00:43:06,300 --> 00:43:08,130
Okay. It's okay with me.

909
00:43:08,480 --> 00:43:10,210
Well, if there's nothing else,

910
00:43:10,450 --> 00:43:11,580
I'll be leaving now.

911
00:43:17,040 --> 00:43:19,890
Look at him—scared stiff like a fool.

